Results

Source: R/results-methods.R
results.Rd

Results

results(object, ...)

# S4 method for FGSEAList
results(object, contrast, collection)

Arguments

object

Object.
contrast

character(1). Contrast name.
collection

character(1). Gene set collection name. Typically refers to h (hallmark), c1-c7 collections from MSigDb. Can obtain using collectionNames() on FGSEAList object.
...

Additional arguments.

Value

Varies, depending on the method.

Note

Updated 2020-09-23.

Examples

data(fgsea)

## FGSEAList ====
results(
    object = fgsea,
    contrast = "condition_B_vs_A",
    collection = "h"
)
